#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:4
msgid "简介：计算x的逐元素softmax。"
msgstr "Introduction: Compute the element-wise softmax of x."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.softmax(x, dim=None, keep_dims=False, ieee_rounding=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `dim`        | `int`          | 指定在哪个维度上计算 softmax                                                      |\n"
"| `keep_dims`        | `bool`          | 控制计算后是否保留原维度的形状                                                  |\n"
"| `ieee_rounding`   | `bool`                 | 控制浮点数运算是否遵循 IEEE 754 标准的舍入规则          |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type               | Description                                                    |\n"
"| ------------- | ------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`           | `tensor`           | Tensor data                                                    |\n"
"| `dim`         | `int`              | Specifies the dimension on which to compute softmax            |\n"
"| `keep_dims`   | `bool`             | Controls whether to retain the original dimension shape after computation |\n"
"| `ieee_rounding` | `bool`           | Controls whether floating-point operations follow IEEE 754 rounding rules |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`x`：与x相同的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`x`: A tensor with the same shape as `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/softmax.md:18
